               <p>I am a <rs id="t17900224-61-viclabel340" type="occupation">merchant</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17900224-61-victim577 t17900224-61-viclabel340"></join>. On the 2d of February I was walking through <placeName id="t17900224-61-crimeloc341">Bell-court</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17900224-61-crimeloc341" type="placeName" value="Bell-court"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17900224-61-crimeloc341" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17900224-61-off338 t17900224-61-crimeloc341"></join>, and all of a sudden I thought something catched my coat, though I neither heard nor saw any body; I turned myself round, and saw the prisoner going away through Bell-court, into Cornhill, walking; I cried out, stop thief! he was stopped: I never lost sight of him; the street constable asked me what was lost; I told him, I lost my handkerchief; I stepped up to him, and he gave me the handkerchief.</p>
               <p>
            
